  "epitaph": "Once, you drew the bounding boxes that taught machines how to see,\nA simple frame to capture truth for deep-learning\u2019s infancy.\nThough the Python script has ceased and the master branch is torn,\nYour legacy is blooming in a Studio, newly born.\nArchived in silence, leaving just a ghost of annotation and fame,\n`git checkout` the future, and forget your former name.\nRest in peace, old window, rest in /dev/null.",
